description:
This is a copy of the voting video I posted two days ago, but without the music that caused it to be blocked in some countries. Here's a repeat of the same video description:

Voting now begins for the 6th annual coveted Golden Crocoduck. The award is given for the biggest breach of the 9th Commandment in pursuit of the creationist cause. Five nominees made it to the final voting list, and I have highlighted them all throughout the year. 
   To vote, please visit http://tiny.cc/crocoduck
